WEBVTT

00:09.759 --> 00:12.262
You're traveling
through another dimension-

00:12.297 --> 00:16.015
a dimension not only of sight
and sound, but of mind,

00:16.050 --> 00:17.267
a journey into a wondrous land

00:17.302 --> 00:19.769
whose boundaries
are that of imagination.

00:19.804 --> 00:22.272
Your next stop,
the twilight zone.

